{"type": "article", "id": 2933, "title": "I Love Ugly 2014眼镜系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-20T08:34:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232415pdkrbZLPUnzlatRq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自新西兰的时尚品牌 I Love Ugly 日前正式进军眼镜领域，为今年秋冬推出了全新眼镜系列。该系列包含平光镜与太阳镜两种类型，设计上延续了品牌一贯的简约风格，并采用了天然棉纤维的醋酸材质制作而成，搭配以侧边的金属细节与 CR-39 镜片，为用户提供 100% 防护紫外线的功能。定价 180-199 美元不等，<a href=\"http://www.iloveugly.net/eyewear.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052324110vNL9fdB4x2skOYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232412OpZGWQf8cTy3Jtvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232412RhKyajYeTVIF5nAw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232413EOnwPRSvz9IMdYgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232413cOMCdhw5WJtRGZ06.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232414N81ZtzqKTMgVRLdU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232414h7wgbZj1sBIWlceP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}